### Impact

Locks of the type `@nonreentrant("")` or `@nonreentrant('')` do not produce reentrancy checks at runtime.

```Vyper
@nonreentrant("") # unprotected
@external
def bar():
    pass

@nonreentrant("lock") # protected
@external
def foo():
    pass
```
### Patches

Patched in #3605

### Workarounds

The lock name should be a non-empty string.

